'''UBH Denton''' (University Behavioral Health of Denton) is a [[Private hospital|Private]] [[Psychiatric Hospital]] Located in [[Denton, Texas]].

UBH Denton provides both [[inpatient]] and [[outpatient]] services, as well as specialty programs for patients with [[mental disorders]], women's [[mental health]] and [[chemical dependency]],  [[pain management]], military-related mental disorders (such as [[PTSD]]), and a program for children and adolescents.<ref>{{cite web|title=Best Hospitals: University Behavioral Health of Denton|url=http://health.usnews.com/best-hospitals/university-behavioral-health-of-denton-6740336/details|publisher=U.S. News}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=UBH Denton Specialty Programs|url=http://www.ubhdenton.com/SpecialtyPrograms.aspx|publisher=Ascend Health}}</ref>

